{[#] The only way to quickly reach the g7-pawn is} 38. Nxh7 $1 {and knight
can't be safely taken.} Kxh7 39. Rxg7+ $1 Kh8 (39... Kxg7 40. Rg3+ {followed
by Qg7#.}) 40. Rcg3 e5 $1 {The best way to defend. Now the only move wins.} 41.
Re7 $18 {I hope you have seen it in advance.} *

