{[#]} 48. Qxe6 $3 {It is not hard to believe that this move works well but it
is way harder to see it in the real game.} Qh4 ({If Black accepts the sacrifice
} 48... dxe6 {nothing can help his king after} 49. Rxf7 Rb7 50. Raxb7 Bxb7 51.
Rxg7+ Kh8 52. Rd7+ $18) 49. Qxf7 Qxf4+ 50. Kg1 {Black resigned because he had
