{[#]} 36. Rxd7 $3 {A stunning tactic. Black is unable to defend all key
squares.} Qxe5+ (36... Qxd7 37. e6 $1 Qxe6 (37... Qd6+ 38. Kh3 Re7 39. Qf6+ Kg8
40. Qf8#) 38. Qd8+ $18) (36... Rxd7 37. Qf6+ Kg8 38. Rd1 $3 $18 {Black has no
a defense.} (38. e6 $4 {leads to a failure} Qe7 $1 {and White is lost.})) 37.
Kh3 Rxd7 38. Re1 $3 {White sacrifices his second rook.} Rg4 {Nice
counterattack, but it leads only to the endgame without a bishop.} (38... Qb8
39. Qf6+ Kg8 40. Qe6+ Rf7 41. Qxc4 $18) (38... Qxe1 39. Qf6+ Kg8 40. Qf8#) 39.
Rxe5 Rxg5 40. Bxg5 $18 *

