{[#]} 38. h6+ $1 ({In the game White played} 38. Re4 $2 {that gave Black a
chance to stabilize a situation by playing} Re7 $1 ({Black missed the chance
and played} 38... g5 $2 $18 {to weaken all squares around the Black king.}))
38... Kxh6 ({Or} 38... Kf8 39. Be6 $1 Re7 40. Qxf6 Rxe6 41. Rxe6 Qxe6 42. Qg7+
Ke7 43. Qxh7 $18) 39. Be6 $1 {The key of a combination.} fxe6 (39... Kg7 40.
Bxd7 Qxd7 41. Qd5 $18) 40. Qxf6 $18 *

