noted that White had brought all his pieces away from the queenside.} 20...
Rxf3 $3 21. Rxf3 {A capture with the g2-pawn would not change anything.} Nb4 $3
({White resigned because after} 21... Nb4 22. axb4 Ba4 {he can't defend on c2.}
