perpetual check. In other cases, White would stay better.} ({There is no time
to take on c2.} 31... Qxc2 $2 32. Be6 $1 $16 {(prevents Re2) and now} Bg1 $4 {
does not work} 33. Rxg1 Qf2 34. Qb3 $18) 32. Rxg1 Qf2 33. Be6 $8 {White should
block the e-file because otherwise Black checkmates (thanks to Re2).} Qh4+ ({
is also drawn} 33... Qxf3+ 34. Kh2 Qe2+ 35. Kh1 Qf3+) 34. Kg2 Qg3+ 35. Kf1
Qxf3+ 36. Ke1 Qe3+ $11 *

